OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSpells of
OL,6,Fhazy sunshine during Friday evening.
OL,7,FCloud building overnight with spots
OL,8,Fof, mostly light, rain possible,
OL,9,Fthough some remaining dry. A mild
OL,10,Fnight for many.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FEarly low cloud quickly
OL,13,Fbreaking and giving way to a dry and
OL,14,Fbright day, although sunshine may be
OL,15,Fslightly hazy at times. Feeling very
OL,16,Fwarm in the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
